title: Ethnicity and Population Estimates, Districts, Eastern Region Afghanistan
name: Ethnicity and Population Estimates, Districts, Eastern Region Afghanistan
description: This is a shapefile showing the different ethnicities and percentages along with population estimates for districts in the Eastern Region of Afghanistan. Data was hand recorded from various PDF files that were sent to each district. This is the amalgamation of these PDF files. Uploaded into GeoIQ as shp, dbf, and shx files.
